老人文娛設施不足問題<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">(五)檢討管理</span><br />\n 要求康文署檢討屯門公園及割下公共空間的管理，有效分配公園及其他公共空間的使用權<br />\n<br />\n交通：<br />\n巴士： <br />\n58M / 58X / 63X / 260X / 960 - 紅橋站落車<br />\n黨鐵：<br />\n1. 西鐵兆康站落車<br />\n2. 轉乘輕鐵 751 (往友愛）或610 （往屯門碼頭）"},{"pid":"d0d29e5671146b55149acd92575a492376d6b40f","tid":1580304,"uid":124045,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"32d92189784b51c103d3055f76595494c221a195","tid":1580304,"uid":4761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:12:00.000Z","msg":"點解要比佢做主場？<br />\n<br />\n下星期同一時間我地中大開壇叫佢過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:14:28.000Z","msg":"自設大台佢過黎好似好傻wor<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可 根本無野好傾<br />\n<br />\n做到就完 做唔到等制裁 係咁多"},{"pid":"ff8532e65db779c65cdd83ca3c6394ee85b2f5df","tid":1580304,"uid":55835,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:14:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家報名啦，咪被代表，同時都表現出我地和理非，會溝通既形象<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9c5ce8ba1c173a76ad978bdc844dcc6c2196c246","tid":1580304,"uid":76960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:14:46.000Z","msg":"開你老母個壇咩<br />\n你都講左四大訴求唔會回應啦，傾乜尻呀，出解放軍行緊急法啦你條死柒婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72aedf44ee218e95614ede7aaa9c1a22722d4fb3","tid":1580304,"uid":252281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f90df4067a99c5a087d0b6a7f0cde19e708faf2","tid":1580304,"uid":164374,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:10:42.000Z","msg":"由得佢地係度圍暖啦<br />\n成日講<br />\n1. 普遍市民主流意見係止暴制亂<br />\n2. 極少數極端暴力示成者<br />\n由佢地慢慢自慰LOR<br />\n同班仆街炒攬就勢在必行<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji